Theorem repbool_list_insert_ts:
  ∀xs m ts_vl ts refs1 seen1 lims.
    repbool_list xs m ts_vl ∧ ts_vl ≤ ts
  ⇒ size_of lims [xs] refs1 (insert ts () seen1) =
     (λ(x,y,z). (x,y,insert ts () z)) (size_of lims [xs] refs1 seen1)
Proof
